# 3D Avatar Website

A simple 3D web app that includes:

- Character loading and animation
- Lip sync
- Face tracking
- Geolocation
- Character customization (color, morphs)

## How to Run

1. Open the folder in VS Code.
2. Install the "Live Server" extension.
3. Right-click `index.html` and click **"Open with Live Server"**.
4. Allow webcam and location access when prompted.

## Assets

- Place your `avatar.glb` in the `assets/` folder.
- Add `lipsync_profile.json` if using wLipSync.

## Tech Used

- [Three.js](https://threejs.org/)
- [MediaPipe Holistic](https://google.github.io/mediapipe/)
- [Kalidokit](https://github.com/yeemachine/kalidokit)